<p><strong><span data-contrast="auto">PR/Socials&nbsp;</span></strong>&nbsp;</p>
<p><span data-contrast="auto">By getting someone to spearhead into PR and solcial relations, we would ensure that we are able to have someone dedicated to developing a positive relationship with clients and potential business partners. By having someone in this role it makes sure that we have an experienced person to maintain relationships between different entities. Having a profesional person maintain these relationships is beneficial by itself, however it also ensures that our other team members are able to focus more heavily on their work, improving their productivity,&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast="auto">and not having to maintain relationships which is time consuming and would detract from completing their other works.</span>&nbsp;</p>
